snippet.title: Tilmbila Live Aid Concert Series - Gest: Thought Universe (aka Mark Pilkington)
snippet.description:
MANTIS FESTIVAL 2020 - 1st November 2020
Our first ever in-game concert at Timbila Live Aid
Absolute madness!! Thank you all the attendees and thank you Mark Pilkington. You are genius.
Production Team: Ricardo Climent (Keep it Human), Alena Mesarosova and Manu Ferrer (Manusamo & Bzika / El Capricho AudioVisual)
